      else:
          self._raf_id = None

5) Optional (extra safety): disable buttons once clicked to prevent rapid re-entries:
- In on_next/on_retry start by disabling the clicked button and re-enable when the level ends, or rely on the RAF guard above.

These changes ensure there is at most one active animation loop, preventing timing drift and performance issues.

